{"tid":566162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡全民派錢 唔識做長遠野","createTime":"2018-02-19T16:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T23:56:17.000Z","uid":143078,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"99635793d0058c7319a55dc476a316eabca47881","tid":566162,"uid":143078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:26:18.000Z","msg":"新加坡政府公布2018/19年度財政預算案，預計去年錄得96億坡元財政盈餘。新加坡財長王瑞傑公布，所有滿21歲國民今年可按收入獲得100至300坡元「紅包」（約600至1,800元），約有270萬人受惠。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新加坡政府建議，年收入達2.8萬坡元（約16.7萬港元）或以下國民可獲派300坡元；年收入10萬坡元（約59.6萬港元）可獲派200坡元；年收入超過10萬坡元或持多個一個物業可獲派100坡元。</span><br />\n<br />\n為應付未來社會於基建及教育等方面的增加開支，預算案亦提出於2021年至2025年間上調消費稅 (GST）兩個百分點，由目前7%增至9%，具體推出時間則視乎當地經濟及開支情況而定。<br />\n此外，新加坡亦計畫課徵每噸5元新幣碳稅（carbon tax）。自2020年起亦會向進口服務課徵e-tax，包括網上影片及音樂串流平台等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180219/57850950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57850950&d=Ux%2BLYFAShSwRtbfuYHZFAzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f3621c79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57850950&h=4778c3ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180219/57850950</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淨係識派錢，博一時掌聲，唔怪得咁落後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586ff0e7a81fc973345d4f530d35b0150f2918f4","tid":566162,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99635793d0058c7319a55dc476a316eabca47881","tid":566162,"uid":143078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:26:18.000Z","msg":"新加坡政府公布2018/19年度財政預算案，預計去年錄得96億坡元財政盈餘。新加坡財長王瑞傑公布，所有滿21歲國民今年可按收入獲得100至300坡元「紅包」（約600至1,800元），約有270萬人受惠。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">新加坡政府建議，年收入達2.8萬坡元（約16.7萬港元）或以下國民可獲派300坡元；年收入10萬坡元（約59.6萬港元）可獲派200坡元；年收入超過10萬坡元或持多個一個物業可獲派100坡元。</span><br />\n<br />\n為應付未來社會於基建及教育等方面的增加開支，預算案亦提出於2021年至2025年間上調消費稅 (GST）兩個百分點，由目前7%增至9%，具體推出時間則視乎當地經濟及開支情況而定。<br />\n此外，新加坡亦計畫課徵每噸5元新幣碳稅（carbon tax）。自2020年起亦會向進口服務課徵e-tax，包括網上影片及音樂串流平台等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180219/57850950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57850950&d=Ux%2BLYFAShSwRtbfuYHZFAzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f3621c79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180219%2F57850950&h=4778c3ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180219/57850950</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淨係識派錢，博一時掌聲，唔怪得咁落後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"大巴大巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50613cbb2a94a7fb272efe70153dedd0021ba8f7","tid":566162,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"手執SGD 好過揸HKD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82ec1e7d75a5757b0d49e36cb4a608f3d4c48a9","tid":566162,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"越有錢派得越少，喺香港實俾人嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05c550934d2f0f13ce2a4b704f359dea9bd003d","tid":566162,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"$600-$1800港元，使得幾耐"},{"pid":"794a646064ba63c407aee88c9d6782835f72131e","tid":566162,"uid":36390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:46:37.000Z","msg":"咁嘅環境都唔批，唔知政府想點"},{"pid":"27de2b0a50f68b412e3352fec7ebc6d189f68e05","tid":566162,"uid":35648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyT